init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She opens the door to find a cat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She decides to name it “He-Man” because of its size and attitude.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She decides to take it with her on her date, but the cat is not happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The cat jumps up on the chair and begins to walk around it, and then jumps down and walks around the table.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman is very upset that her date is late, and she is also upset that the cat is not happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The cat eats it and then jumps up on the chair again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She orders a steak, and when it comes, she offers it to the cat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He hands it to her and says, “This was delivered for you a while ago.”

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have been here since 8:00 and I am sitting in the cat's chair.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am not a cat, but a shapeshifter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have been trying to get it right, but I never seem to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I will be your best friend for life!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She leaves the restaurant and heads for home.
